::Spears::

She turned and looked at Striker through the hole in the cell 
door. "I am now the property of Master Prebon.  I can not leave him 
now."  She looked at Striker, "It's the price one pays when you love 
someone."  She immediately turned her back to him.  She couldn't take 
much more of htis torture.  It was tearing her apart inside.
